                Secondly; His personal fitness: Of his fulness we all receive
grace for grace, In him are hid all the treasures of wisdom;
and then

                3. Give him the honor of his Riches and Fulness, seek supplies
from him, do not live upon your selves, nor upon your duties,
nor upon ordinances onely, but live upon Jesus Christ in all,
so give Christ the honor of being the spring of your Supplies;
in him are fresh springs.

4. The end of the world: What, to the end of this Dispensation, and for the age of this Ministration only? brethren, I could fetch it out of the very Original it self;
